Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:09.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　エラムが私をかばい　手傷を負ってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Elam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:10.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,エラムが…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This was thoughtless invasion for glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,功を急いた無謀な突撃だった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the guy temperamental.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの少年の気性なのだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.01,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,覚えているだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyusitanianets, which we released when he took me to the hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:23.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,かつて私が人質にされたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,取り逃がしたルシタニアの少年だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:28.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As if ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:30.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あのときと同じく…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Although now his gaze was even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:34.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　今はそれ以上に険しい瞳をしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun. Narsus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン　ナルサス
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I also sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:40.83,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私も出るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince goes into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:57.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下がご出陣を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If in this battle we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,戦況が五分だというのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the king must go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:05.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今こそ王が先頭に立ち　皆を励まし　奮い立たせるべきだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to inspire people and raise their morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It is unlikely that I will do so, as her father,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,父上のようにはできないだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but for those who suffer in combat,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:11.63,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今日まで傷ついてきた皆のためにも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go into battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私は出陣したい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Narsus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:18.41,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサス様　アルフリード様より報告です
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Report from the Alfred mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:19.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,来たか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She reports that will open the gates at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,夜明けとともに城門を開けるとのことです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:24.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,承知した
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We are a key element in this battle. So do not hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:34.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私らがこの戦の要　ひるむんじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On the day of my first battle of Atropatena,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:02.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アトロパテネの初陣の日　私は敗走した
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in deep despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,絶望の淵にあったが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but here today,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:06.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because with me Daryun, Narsus and my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:10.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューンや　ナルサスや　そして　ここにいる全ての者が
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:12.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私を支えてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:17.26,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,皆と共にエクバタナを奪還する
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Together we will refund Ecbatana,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:21.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そして　私は皆の王となろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,will your King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Castle Defense is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:26.10,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,城の守りは強固だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:30.69,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だが今　味方の決死隊が敵の隠し道から侵入し
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,we boldly go through a secret passage to the enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and with the coming of dawn break through the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,夜明けとともに門を破る
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Parsis gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:45.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスの神々よ　あまたの英霊たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And the souls of our fallen heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you, provide us with support in this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:49.93,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,願わくば　我らにお力を貸したまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Jasasuiin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:52.33,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤシャスィーン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:03.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,来たぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:05.59,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:16.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Open the gates before the sun fully rises!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:29.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,急げ　朝日が昇りきるまでに城門を開けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:31.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こ…こいつら　どこから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did they come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not panic! They are few!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.19,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,慌てるな　寡兵だ　下の兵を呼んで…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,gather the people from below and ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Support our inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.07,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,突入部隊を援護しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sudden attack on the gates of the castle ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,城門上に奇襲だと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Send to the people and to repel the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,早く兵を回し　鎮圧しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If they open the gates, and we are not last minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:53.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,門を開かれたら　一刻と　もたんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Zaravant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ザラーヴァント様
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gates began to open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:00.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,門が開きはじめましたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the gate open?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,な…なぜ　城門が開いている
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather people in a castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:07.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,城の兵を集めよ　門の内側に壁を…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Create a wall at the gate ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon there will be the main army!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:12.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに本隊が来るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit more! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:15.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あと少しだ　頑張れ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pushes them! You can not miss ... more
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:22.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お…押し返せ　これ以上　中に入れては…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:41.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To deploy troops on the left and right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.52,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,部隊を左右に展開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We come to the castle gate, and pushed the enemy troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:58.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,城門を駆け上がって　敵兵を制圧せよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The main forces do not stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:03.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,主力部隊は足を止めるな　そのまま本城を落とせ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rushes and capture the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Narsus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:05.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサス
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:24.69,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,来ましたな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,来るぞ　これ以上　進ませるな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Do not pass them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:35.47,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン　キシュワード　遠慮はいらん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun! Kisvard! Do not hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:51.43,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:54.67,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,挟撃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At both sides?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:56.30,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下を守れ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect the prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:08.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:11.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,クバード
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuʙard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:15.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン王子　随分とりりしくなられた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Lions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You are such a valiant warrior steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,駆けつけた甲斐もあったというもの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have decided that it is worth to join you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:20.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　行かれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ご自身が真の王だと言われるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're applying for something to be a real king,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:26.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ご自分自身で示さねばなりませぬぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you will have to prove it on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.09,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,抜けたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:32.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　進みましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャスワント　頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaswant, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:35.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,生きていたら　酒でもおごれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you survive, be sure to buy me wine, Daryun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,見えたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.73,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,サームか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:11:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Milk powder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.52,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:14.97,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,行きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Idemte!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:23.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサス
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Narsus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:24.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,行け
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.26,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,立ち止まれば　こやつの隊に包囲されるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stop, you will immediately be surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:30.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサス　死ぬなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Narsus ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It will depend on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それはお主らしだいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:49.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,イアルダボート神よ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,God Ialdabaoth ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:13:00.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,所詮はギスカールの借り物どもよ　いくら数を減らそうがかまわん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like people Giscard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not care how poredeyut their ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,むしろルシタニアにとっても程よい痛手となろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyusitaniya suffer heavy losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:08.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,来い　アンドラゴラスの小せがれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Invoked offspring Andragorasa ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You suffer a humiliation in front of his subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:14.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様は忠臣たちの前に最大の屈辱をさらすことになるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　あとは私が
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, I'll deal with the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　私が行かねばならない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この先に従兄弟殿がいるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They were hiding my cousin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:42.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ファランギース
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Farangis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,With me the divine protection of Mithras.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:45.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私にはミスラ神の加護があります
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:49.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,汚れた邪教の矢が私に当たることなどありえませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrows of corrupt heretics will not get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:55.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そして殿下　あなたにも神のご加護があります
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And the prince, this divine protection extends to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:58.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,非道な輩に悔い改めさせることができるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that you and only you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:02.53,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下において他にないと私は思っております
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to send these barbarous people to the true path.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お行きください
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:10.99,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下の行く先　敵は全て私が射抜いてさしあげましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,there I was fighting all the enemies with his arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　行きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン王子か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Prince Arslan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ子供ではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Still just a kid ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:55.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり黒衣の騎士と一緒か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Still came with a black knight, as I waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ペシャワールの夜以来になるな　従兄弟殿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not seen since the night in Peshavarde, dear brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:04.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,従兄弟などと呼ばれるのは汚らわしいが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to hear from your lips the word "brother", but the fellow that came.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:05.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よく来た
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:13.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さぞや　今日ここにたどりつくまでに苦しんだことであろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you had suffered a great deal as was getting here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:15.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:17.63,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,耳を貸してはなりませぬぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not pay any attention to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:18.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:21.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私は彼の話が聞きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:23.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:29.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,苦悩を乗り越え　私に追いついたとでも思っているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that having overcome all difficulties, you become a match for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:31.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,笑わせるな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:36.29,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お前はここで無残に討ち死にし　醜態をさらすことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You in this game is waiting for the tragic death and disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:41.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも　私が受けた屈辱に足りるものではない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But still,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it does not compare to the humiliation that I have experienced!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:44.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私の怒りが収まりはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My anger will never end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:49.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様はそんな逆恨みで　ずっと殿下を追い詰めていたというのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to some unjustified resentment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you all the while pursued Prince ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.29,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,逆恨みだと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Unjustified insults ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:54.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この癒えぬ傷の痛み　貴様に分かるものか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never understand the pain unhealed wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:55.52,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,分かります
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:59.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　傷ついているのはあなただけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But you do not suffer alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.69,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスの民　皆だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,People Parsis too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:08.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが国を思う正統な血縁だというのなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,proclaims itself the true king,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:12.99,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだろう　私に力を貸してはくれないだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you like this:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,if you agree to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:18.15,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王位を譲る…　とは言わぬのだな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you are not going to yield to my throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今や私にも背負うものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,At me now the responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:25.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,皆の望みと私の望みは同じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire of the people the same as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,サーム様　もうダメです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Saam, we do not hold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒルメス殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Hermes ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,退け　退け
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:40.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私がパルスの王を継ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be worthy of the king of Parsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:44.49,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,国と民を思う気持ちはあなたと違いない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My attitude to the kingdom and its people is different from yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:54.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　今の言葉　しかと胸に刻みました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, your words will remain forever in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:56.03,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:59.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたの家臣でよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:06.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様ら　どこまで私をイラつかせる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How much you will still pour oil into the fire ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:12.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,不浄の血縁　それに味方する貴様らはパルス騎士の恥さらしよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He is not a descendant of the royal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And you bastards, serving him only disgrace the knights Parsis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.73,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下を愚弄することは許さん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not allow to insult the prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:22.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.41,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,バルカシオン伯爵ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Barkasion, I believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:31.59,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さよう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:37.39,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,此度　多くの家臣を失った　戦などつらいことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost a lot of people in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,War is always cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:41.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　早く終わらせなければならないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we should as soon as possible to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:47.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたはお優しい王なのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you will become a good king.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:51.93,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,イアルダボート教は他の信徒は認めない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith Yaldabaoth not accept other believers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:54.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何百年も変わらなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This has not changed for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:57.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,果たして方法がありますかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:17:58.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:06.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,惜しいな　マルダーン・フ・マルダーン
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame, Mardan Mardan fu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have sent its strength at the service of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:09.66,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その力　正統の王のために…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,使えばよかったものを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the true King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:17.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,断じてありえん　我が王はアルスラーン殿下のみ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My king - Prince Arslan and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:36.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,信念に突き動かされた忌々しい目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your glare accompanied by confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:40.61,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,証明してみせようではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I show you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,誰が正しいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do wrong ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:50.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ殺さぬ　お前たちが心の底から負けたと思わないかぎりな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,While you are with all your heart does not acknowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that definitively lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでなければ　意味がない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, everything will be useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:59.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでなくては　私の怒りが収まることはないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:20:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, my rage will never die down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:04.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,待て…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay! ..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:26.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:29.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,バルカシオン伯爵様
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Barkasion graph ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that the fall of the castle is already inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:36.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もはや落城は避けられぬようじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:40.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,降伏…　してはくださいませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You agree to give up ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:47.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,無駄に殺すな　我々は文明国であるパルスの民だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Without useless bloodshed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We the people Parsis, a civilized country!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:50.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,略奪もならん　固く命じる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No looting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:05.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.33,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,伯爵　戦いは終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Graf, the battle is over! Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,皆を止めてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:21.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,優しい異教の王子よ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good King of the Gentiles,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:25.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だからといって　止められるものではありませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it was, it did not stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:28.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,信仰とはそういうものです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Such is the nature of the believer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:30.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:35.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私にできることは皆と　そして神と共にあることです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,be with the people and our Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:38.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜだ　せっかく助かる命だというのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! You do save lives! Why would you want to die ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして死ななければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:09.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:10.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:23.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,伯爵様を殺したのは　お前か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you kill Mr. Earl?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.15,0:22:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,YakuSub Studio
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.06,0:22:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,translation Mu_Cool
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,kimi ga deatta kokoro wa kitto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All the souls that you could meet on the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,hitotsu datte machigai janai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly it was pure and innocent,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.10,0:22:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Editorial Mu_Cool
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.06,0:22:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,onaji yume wo daite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.06,0:22:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We kept the same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.23,0:22:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Making Weekend
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,michi wo tagaeta hito wo omotta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,People walking different paths,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.73,0:22:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,nozarashi no akogare wo kakagete susumu kouya
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.73,0:22:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,killed all my hopes and desires revive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.49,0:23:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,hohoemi mo sono namida mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.49,0:23:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile on his face, tears running down her cheeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,koko ni suteteyukenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to go ahead, they should not be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,kage wo daite shiroku takaku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Covered by the shadow of the summer, so white and immense,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,namonaki boku to kimi no hata
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,our with you nameless flag flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,mada hatenaku tsudzuku kono mich ino kanata ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There, on the road, which extends an endless path,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,tatta hitotsu no hikari wo sen no kokoro ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one bright light, and with it a thousand souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.83,0:23:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,miageru sora wo shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.83,0:23:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in the sky above his head,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,michibiku hoshi wo higashi no takami ni sashishimesu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there putevodnaâ our star in the east, ee do not engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.16,0:23:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,yume wa kono te de kanaeru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.16,0:23:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And their cherished dream in flesh forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:24:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Estelle eyes shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:01.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,エステルの目から　涙がこぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.04,0:24:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of countless deaths and tragic death
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.31,0:24:04.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,無数の悲惨な死が積み重ねられた末に
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a new birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.38,0:24:06.41,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,一つの誕生が訪れた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time:. "The way out of the blood and sweat"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:09.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,次回　汗血公路
